\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"evVc7dK3Ps\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/17/introducing-createinterpolateelement/\">Introducing createInterpolateElement</a></blockquote><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"&#8220;Introducing createInterpolateElement&#8221; &#8212; Make WordPress Core\" src=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/17/introducing-createinterpolateelement/embed/#?secret=evVc7dK3Ps\" data-secret=\"evVc7dK3Ps\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-make-wordpress-core\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"asxklld9KJ\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/24/new-wp_get_environment_type-function-in-wordpress-5-5/\">New wp_get_environment_type() function in WordPress 5.5</a></blockquote><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"&#8220;New wp_get_environment_type() function in WordPress 5.5&#8221; &#8212; Make WordPress Core\" src=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/24/new-wp_get_environment_type-function-in-wordpress-5-5/embed/#?secret=asxklld9KJ\" data-secret=\"asxklld9KJ\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-make-wordpress-core\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"WIcHBVPlvS\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/06/26/wordpress-5-5-better-fine-grained-control-of-redirect_guess_404_permalink/\">WordPress 5.5: Better fine grained control of redirect_guess_404_permalink()</a></blockquote><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"&#8220;WordPress 5.5: Better fine grained control of redirect_guess_404_permalink()&#8221; &#8212; Make WordPress Core\" src=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/06/26/wordpress-5-5-better-fine-grained-control-of-redirect_guess_404_permalink/embed/#?secret=WIcHBVPlvS\" data-secret=\"WIcHBVPlvS\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-make-wordpress-core\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"vyzUmEVDIk\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/10/new-css-styles-for-buttons-with-disabled-state-in-wp-5-5/\">New CSS styles for buttons with disabled state in WP 5.5</a></blockquote><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"&#8220;New CSS styles for buttons with disabled state in WP 5.5&#8221; &#8212; Make WordPress Core\" src=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/10/new-css-styles-for-buttons-with-disabled-state-in-wp-5-5/embed/#?secret=vyzUmEVDIk\" data-secret=\"vyzUmEVDIk\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-make-wordpress-core\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"SknizKJZ2e\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/15/dashicons-in-wordpress-5-5-the-final-update/\">Dashicons in WordPress 5.5 (the final update)</a></blockquote><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"&#8220;Dashicons in WordPress 5.5 (the final update)&#8221; &#8212; Make WordPress Core\" src=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/15/dashicons-in-wordpress-5-5-the-final-update/embed/#?secret=SknizKJZ2e\" data-secret=\"SknizKJZ2e\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-make-wordpress-core\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"hXuSi5pXMM\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/14/php-related-improvements-changes-wordpress-5-5-edition/\">PHP related improvements &amp; changes: WordPress 5.5 edition</a></blockquote><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"&#8220;PHP related improvements &amp; changes: WordPress 5.5 edition&#8221; &#8212; Make WordPress Core\" src=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/14/php-related-improvements-changes-wordpress-5-5-edition/embed/#?secret=hXuSi5pXMM\" data-secret=\"hXuSi5pXMM\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Et pour finir, un petit florilège de modifications diverses et variées</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Cela fait en tout <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?status=closed&amp;type=defect+(bug)&amp;milestone=5.5&amp;group=component&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=type&amp;col=owner&amp;col=priority&amp;col=component&amp;col=version&amp;order=priority\">306 correctifs</a>, <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?status=closed&amp;type=enhancement&amp;milestone=5.5&amp;group=component&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=type&amp;col=owner&amp;col=priority&amp;col=component&amp;col=version&amp;order=priority\">157 améliorations et nouvelles fonctionnalités</a> et <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?status=closed&amp;type=task+(blessed)&amp;milestone=5.4&amp;group=component&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=type&amp;col=owner&amp;col=priority&amp;col=component&amp;col=version&amp;order=priority\">12 tâches de gestion courante</a> qui ont été marqués <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?status=closed&amp;milestone=5.5&amp;group=component&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=owner&amp;col=type&amp;col=priority&amp;col=component&amp;col=version&amp;order=priority\">comme étant clôturés</a> dans le jalon <code>5.5</code> de WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nous souhaitons également mettre en évidence quelques changements qui n&rsquo;ont pas fait l&rsquo;objet de notes de développement spécifiques (cliquer sur le numéro de ticket pour accéder au ticket en question sur Trac)&nbsp;:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Commentaires : le calcul des nombres de commentaires et de la pagination a été corrigé pour les commentaires non approuvés – <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/8973\">#8973</a></li><li>Commentaires : <code>get_comment_count()</code> retourne maintenant toujours un entier numérique, quelque soit l’état du commentaire – <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/48093\">#48093</a></li><li>Outil de personnalisation (customizer) : l&rsquo;interface de l&rsquo;outil de personnalisation s&rsquo;adapte maintenant en fonction des couleurs alternatives éventuellement choisies pour l&rsquo;interface d&rsquo;administration – <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/50547\">#50547</a></li><li>Internationalisation : des crochets ont été ajoutés pour le filtrage par <code>text-domain</code> des chaînes traduisibles – <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/49518\">#49518</a></li><li>Médias : <code>sanitize_file_name()</code> nettoie désormais correctement les noms de fichier et supprime leurs accents – <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/22363\">#22363</a></li><li>Menus : les réglages des menus sont maintenant directement affichés lors de la création d&rsquo;un nouveau menu – <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/44286\">#44286</a></li><li>Menus : les termes de taxonomies n&rsquo;ayant aucune publication s&rsquo;affichent maintenant dans les résultats de la recherche lors de l&rsquo;ajout d&rsquo;éléments dans les menus de navigation – <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/45298\">#45298</a></li><li>Options, API WordPress.org : les valeurs de métadonnées par défaut sont maintenant supportées – <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/43941\">#43941</a></li><li>Widgets : les widgets utilisant des tailles d&rsquo;images personnalisées affichent maintenant correctement leur légende éventuelle – <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/50160\">#50160</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" />\n\n\n\n<p>Pour rappel, la sortie de WordPress 5.5 est prévue le 11 août 2020. Vous pouvez d’ores et déjà la tester en version&nbsp;<em>Release Candidate</em>&nbsp;en installant l’extension officielle WordPress Beta Tester puis en allant dans ses réglages et en cochant la case&nbsp;Beta/ version de développement puis en mettant à jour votre installation de façon classique.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-plugin-directory\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"dqGKFt2TE9\"><a href=\"https://fr.wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-beta-tester/\">WordPress Beta Tester</a></blockquote><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"« WordPress Beta Tester » &#8212; Plugin Directory\" src=\"https://fr.wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-beta-tester/embed/#?secret=dqGKFt2TE9\" data-secret=\"dqGKFt2TE9\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" />\n\n\n\n<p>Cet article est une traduction du <em><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/30/wordpress-5-5-field-guide/\">Field Guide</a></em><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/30/wordpress-5-5-field-guide/\"> (en anglais)</a> de WordPress 5.5, réalisée par <a href=\"https://profile.wordpress.org/audrasjb\">Jb Audras</a> et relue par <a href=\"https://profile.wordpress.org/chaton666\">Marie Comet</a>, <a href=\"https://profile.wordpress.org/bastho\">Bastien Ho</a> et <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/wolforg\">Wolforg</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:94:\"https://fr.wordpress.org/2020/07/31/les-changements-techniques-a-venir-sur-wordpress-5-5/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:35:\"https://fr.wordpress.org/news/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http: